==English==

===Etymology===
From the [[Hindi]] ''चटनी'' (chaṭnī)

===Noun===
'''chutney''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

# A [[sweet]] or [[savory]] but usually [[spicy]] [[condiment]], originally from eastern [[India]], made from a variety of [[fruit]]s and/or [[vegetable]]s, often containing significant amounts of fresh green [[chili pepper]]s.

